e shares) and Credit Suisse=E2=80=99s AT1 holders are getting nothing: The =
Credit Suisse AT1 securities are getting zeroed. This is not, to be clear, =
exactly because Credit Suisse=E2=80=99s CET1 capital fell below 7%; instead=
