zeroed, because they had the simple heuristic that bonds are always senior =
to stock.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That's the trick! The trick of the AT1s =E2=80=
=94=C2=A0the reason that banks and regulators like them =E2=80=94=C2=A0is t=
